Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  「美幸的鄰居」就是指小南啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？不夠？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  難道說你忘了把自己算進去了…
