Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊的  大家繼續看吧
